How to play

Send a boost to your favourite podcast on Fountain and you could be a winner. The top boost (by value) every week will win a Trezor Model One. Winners will be announced every Friday on Fountain's Twitter.

Download the Fountain app

Fountain is the podcast app that pays and is available on iOS or Android

Top up your Fountain wallet

Go to your Wallet, press Fund Wallet and top up with a bank card or any Lightning Wallet

Boost your favourite show

Show your support for your favourite podcast by sending a boost
BALLER TIP

Connect your ZEBEDEE account to increase your limits

You cannot send a boost larger than 600,000 sats without connecting to a ZEBEDEE account. You will find the option to connect to ZEBEDEE in your Wallet or Profile menu. Simply the follow the steps to create a new account or to connect to an existing one. Once you have done this, the maximum amount you can Boost is increased to 1,000,000 sats.
Learn more
